abstract: As the years passed and as Aung San Suu Kyi remained quiet while under house arrest, many wondered, did she even have a plan? Or was she just a weary goddess, beaten down by the junta in Myanmar? With her apparent election to Parliament, we seem to have an answer.

headline.main: Now, Will She Kick the Hornet's Nest?
